headline: Rhino Resources, Halliburton complete two exploration wells in Block 2914 in Namibia
summary: This marks a significant milestone as these wells are the first to be completed entirely using in-country infrastructure.

headline: Halliburton & Rhino Deliver Two Exploration Wells in Namibia
